generalComment.value:
Site-specific data for the Company processes in the year 2020 - Database Ecoinvent 3.6 - Italian energy mix - Geographical, technological and about system boundaries equivalence for generic data - Impact of proxy data < 10% of the total impact


The allocation of all phases was made for the amount of material sold in 2020 for the different product types in the different materials, coating types, thicknesses and drilling percentages. Based on this data, the following was calculated the impact of the declared unit of 1 square metre of metal ceiling.

A cut-off threshold of 5% was considered for the study, within which they were included:
- the clip inside the "hidden on 60*60", "hidden on 60*120" and "DB
Access": this is an integral component of the structure weighing less than 5% of the total weight of the relevant structure;
- the transparent film protecting the pre-painted coils;
- labels on the packaging of the finished product.

technologicalApplicability.value:
The study is carried out for all families of metal ceilings produced by Profilsystem S.r.l., namely: panels and systems, open cells, planks and structures
 "Products consist of a prepainted or raw metal sheet (steel or aluminium in case of panels, systems and planks; aluminium in case of open cells; steel in case of structures) which is bent, notched and, if necessary, perforated and painted according to the characteristics of the product requested."
